<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="HR0002" sponsor="Melissa G. Ballard" designation="HR" otherSponsor="Stephanie Pitcher" otherHouse="Senate" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL1096" date="01-26-26" printDate="01-26 08:42" subVer="-2" minVer="1" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="hrules"><info><nextbuid>3</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="01/01/1800"><seclist><sect action="A" src="rule" buid="1" uid="HR3-2-S402_1800010118000101" fromuid="HR3-2-S402_2024022220240501" sort="H03 02 04020018000101" mtype="section" effdate="01/01/1800">HR3-2-402</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="2" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="01/01/1800"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>1</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">House Rules Resolution - Standing Committee Duties</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Melissa G. Ballard</sponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This rules resolution modifies the duties of a House standing committee.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This resolution:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">defines terms;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">when considering legislation that proposes to make an occupation a regulated occupation, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10"/>requires a House standing committee to determine whether the Office of Professional <ln numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11"/>Licensure Review conducted a sunrise review of the occupation; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12" level="1">makes technical and conforming changes.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="14">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="16">None</ocNone><ra numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17">Legislative Rules Affected:<raamd numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18"><snhead>AMENDS:</snhead><sn num="HR3-2-402" src="rule" uid="HR3-2-S402_1800010118000101" buid="1" sort="H03 02 04020018000101" numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"><bold>HR3-2-402</bold></sn></raamd></ra></lt><enacthead lineno="20"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="0-21">Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="1" num="HR3-2-402" type="amend" src="rule" uid="HR3-2-S402_1800010118000101" sort="H03 02 04020018000101" numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section number="HR3-2-402" numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-2" type="amend"><secline lineno="22">Section 1. <bold>HR3-2-402</bold> is amended to read:</secline><catline lineno="23"><bold>HR3-2-402<parens/>. Standing committee consideration of legislation -- Regulated <ln numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-3"/>occupation -- Fiscal impact.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="1-null-1" dnum="1-o" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-4" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display>(1)</display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="26" groupid="22" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both">As used in this rule:</amend><subsection ssid="1-8" dnum="_-o:a-e" numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-5" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="admin" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="47" groupid="39" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="end">"Office" means the Office of Professional Licensure Review created in Utah Code <ln numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-6"/>Title 13, Chapter 1b, Office of Professional Licensure Review.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-11" dnum="_-o:b-e" numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-7" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="admin" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="41" groupid="34" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="end">"Regulated occupation" means the same as that term is defined in Utah Code Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="13-1b-101"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-8"/>13-1b-101</xref>.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-12" dnum="_-o:2-e" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-9" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="admin" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="46" groupid="38" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="end">When considering legislation that proposes to make an occupation a regulated <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-10"/>occupation, a standing committee shall determine whether the office conducted a sunrise <ln numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-11"/>review of the occupation in accordance with Utah Code Title 13, Chapter 1b, Part 3, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-12"/>Office Review and Reporting.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-7" dnum="_-o:3-e" numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="admin" style="1" level="1" space="false"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><subsection ssid="1-6" dnum="_-o:a-e" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="admin" style="1" level="2" placement="sameline" space="false"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="end">(a)</amend></display><subsection ssid="1-null-2" dnum="a-o:i-e" level="3" tab="1" placement="sameline"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1006" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(a)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(i)</amend></display>A standing committee may not <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="58" groupid="50" style="2" owner="admin" level="1" deltag="both">review</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="53" groupid="45" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">consider</amend> legislation unless the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-14"/>legislation has an approved fiscal note.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-3" dnum="b-o:ii-e" numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-15" level="3" tab="1"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1007" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(b)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(ii)</amend></display>Notwithstanding Subsection <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="60" groupid="52" style="2" owner="admin" level="1" deltag="both">(1)(a)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="54" groupid="46" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true"><xref depth="4" refnumber="HR3-2-402(3)(a)(i)">(3)(a)(i)</xref></amend>, a standing committee may <ln numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-16"/>consider a substitute not previously adopted, regardless of whether the substitute <ln numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-17"/>has an approved fiscal note.</subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-4" dnum="2-o:b-e" numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-18" level="2"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1008" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(2)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1009" style="1" owner="e" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(b)</amend></display>Except as provided in <xref depth="3" refnumber="HR3-2-401">HR3-2-401</xref>, a standing committee in one or both <ln numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-19"/>chambers shall <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="61" groupid="53" style="2" owner="admin" level="1" deltag="both">review</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="55" groupid="47" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">consider</amend> legislation before the legislation is held in the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-20"/>opposite chamber because of the legislation's fiscal impact.</subsection></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="2" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="false" numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="42">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="43"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both">This resolution takes effect upon a successful vote for final passage.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>1-26-26 7:37 AM</tm></rev></foot></leg>